Reality TV star, Tokunbo Idowu aka TBoss has shared her opinion on people fond of posting Bible quotes and motivational/inspirational posts on social media. According to the 38-year-old media personality, these set of persons are by far the most wicked and toxic humans.   Filmmaker Edgard Leroy dies in auto crash     I was a blind baby when I criticised Tinubu – Mr…     I don’t sing for money but to win souls –Awolumate   Though the reason behind TBoss’ assertion remains unclear, she made this known via an insta story post. “It be the ones always posting up the bible quotes, Motivational & inspiration posts that be the most wicked and toxic… Every Single Time,” the mother of one wrote.